## Web Asset Manager

All CSS and JS **must** be registered through `joomla.asset.json` and loaded via the Web Asset Manager. Never use raw `<link>` or `<script>` tags in templates.

### Registration (joomla.asset.json)

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://developer.joomla.org/schemas/json-schema/web_assets.json",
  "name": "tpl_{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "{{TEMPLATE_NAME}} template assets",
  "license": "GPL-2.0-or-later",
  "assets": [
    {
      "name": "template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}.css",
      "type": "style",
      "uri": "templates/{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}/css/template.css",
      "version": "auto"
    },
    {
      "name": "template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}.js",
      "type": "script",
      "uri": "templates/{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}/js/template.js",
      "dependencies": ["jquery"],
      "attributes": { "defer": true }
    },
    {
      "name": "template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}",
      "type": "preset",
      "dependencies": [
        "template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}.css",
        "template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}.js"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

### Usage (index.php)

```php
$wa = $this->getWebAssetManager();
$wa->usePreset('template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}');
// Or individually:
// $wa->useStyle('template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}.css');
// $wa->useScript('template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}.js');
```

### Asset Naming Convention

- Template preset: `template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}`
- Template styles: `template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}.css`
- Template scripts: `template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}.js`
- Page-specific: `template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}.{page}.css`

**URI convention**: For assets inside a template directory, use `templates/{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}/css/file.css` (full relative path). For assets in the media directory, use `com_example/file.js` (Joomla prepends `js/`/`css/` automatically — do NOT include those subdirectories in the URI).

## Template Entry Point (index.php)

### Minimal Joomla 5 Template

```php
<?php
defined('_JEXEC') or die;

use Joomla\CMS\Document\HtmlDocument;
use Joomla\CMS\Factory;
use Joomla\CMS\HTML\HTMLHelper;
use Joomla\CMS\Uri\Uri;

/** @var HtmlDocument $this */

$app   = Factory::getApplication();
$wa    = $this->getWebAssetManager();
$input = $app->getInput();

// Load template assets
$wa->usePreset('template.{{TEMPLATE_NAME}}');

// Template parameters
$params = $this->params;
?>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<?php echo $this->language; ?>" dir="<?php echo $this->direction; ?>">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <jdoc:include type="metas" />
    <jdoc:include type="styles" />
    <jdoc:include type="scripts" />
</head>
<body class="<?php echo $this->direction === 'rtl' ? 'rtl' : ''; ?>">
    <a href="#main-content" class="visually-hidden-focusable">Skip to main content</a>

    <header>
        <jdoc:include type="modules" name="topbar" style="none" />
        <nav>
            <jdoc:include type="modules" name="menu" style="none" />
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main id="main-content">
        <jdoc:include type="modules" name="breadcrumbs" style="none" />
        <jdoc:include type="message" />
        <jdoc:include type="component" />
    </main>

    <aside>
        <jdoc:include type="modules" name="sidebar" style="card" />
    </aside>

    <footer>
        <jdoc:include type="modules" name="footer" style="none" />
    </footer>

    <jdoc:include type="modules" name="debug" style="none" />
</body>
</html>
```

### Module Positions

Document all module positions and their intended use:

| Position | Location | Typical Content |
|----------|----------|-----------------|
| `topbar` | Above header | Top bar / utility nav |
| `menu` | Header nav area | Main navigation |
| `breadcrumbs` | Below header | Breadcrumb trail |
| `sidebar` | Beside content | Sidebar modules |
| `footer` | Page footer | Footer content |
| `debug` | After footer | Debug module (dev only) |

